@abstract:
Declared intent and purpose for Polyglotformalisms.Jl.
@end

## Purpose

Polyglotformalisms.Jl — **Julia reference implementation of the aggregate-library (PolyglotFormalisms) Common Library with formal verification.*

## Anti-Purpose

This project is NOT:
- A fork or wrapper around another tool
- A monorepo (unless explicitly structured as one)

## If In Doubt

If you are unsure whether a change is in scope, ask.
Sensitive areas: ABI definitions, license headers, CI workflows.
